text: == Births == * Date uncertain – Margaret, the Maid of Norway (died 1290) == Deaths == * January 9 – Wen Tianxiang, Chinese prime minister (executed, born 1236) * October 3 – Dafydd ap Gruffydd, Welsh Prince of Gwynedd (executed) * Philip, Crown Prince of Constantinople, Persian poet (born 1243) * Piotr z Bogorii i Skotnik, Polish nobleman
